    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package on the basis that Monte Carlo UQ bounds on hemolysis index remain below the absolute clinical threshold across all assessed operating points, and that the identified gaps are documented for follow-on study. The ContextOfUse description enumerates flow rates, pressures, speeds, temperature, and hematocrit ranges in narrative form, which the team treated as sufficient specification of the operating domain. No formal hasOperatingEnvelope or hasApplicabilityConstraint constraint was linked, leaving the bounded range of valid model use technically unspecified per W-ON-02.",
